{"tid":2032374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"立國安法及國歌法後，最懷情況係","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T05:32:27.000Z","uid":149978,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a180fba6be0966f970b10cbddaebcf6fb8b60e","tid":2032374,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"大量外資走晒<br />\n大量中資投入<br />\n樓價照高企<br />\n人工照低<br />\n大學生繼續乞食<br />\n大陸人落黎香港歧視返香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就最sad"},{"pid":"2af7fa72d82a576c1cece0406a5fc8297b03d277","tid":2032374,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8a180fba6be0966f970b10cbddaebcf6fb8b60e","tid":2032374,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"大量外資走晒<br />\n大量中資投入<br />\n樓價照高企<br />\n人工照低<br />\n大學生繼續乞食<br />\n大陸人落黎香港歧視返香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就最sad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"大家攬炒既對象唔同"},{"pid":"ee878b104b17faf959f0b2ed27b678668506d0b1","tid":2032374,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"所以一定要成功攬炒速成支爆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=b1e55bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"37cacfc6740a1781129cdf46975ee831ba74654b","tid":2032374,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"呢個有冇國安法都出現緊"},{"pid":"e3c2d54bf390073b0f624674deb3c5337105300d","tid":2032374,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"睇一睇樓主紀錄<br />\n<br />\n係放負五毛黎 最鍾意貼大公<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"22c8e404c550e5e3487317089117409aa344ca54","tid":2032374,"uid":189638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"外資走晒，咁即係港美關係法都冇撚咗，中資仲嚟香港把柒？"},{"pid":"f8e7c62b264494c27418f9cc4e34179b5e84a044","tid":2032374,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"22c8e404c550e5e3487317089117409aa344ca54","tid":2032374,"uid":189638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"外資走晒，咁即係港美關係法都冇撚咗，中資仲嚟香港把柒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"托市，托住香港<br />\n中國人最要面<br />\n證明冇左外國，香港一樣得"},{"pid":"bd3898678dd4d59ed3cba205c97d76cef471c226","tid":2032374,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"大量外資走晒一定<br />\n但大量中資投入就唔一定<br />\n無左特殊地位<br />\n中資仲黎投資做乜？"},{"pid":"ab6be32b72155e4a3ea0779bc8c30fe3034e0923","tid":2032374,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8e7c62b264494c